# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_MAGNET_STRENGTH

## Summary
Set the overall strength of the magnet force that is applied to the entity that is being picked up

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **FLOAT** magnetStrength
